oulton Fountain">Doulton Fountain</a> at <a href="/wiki/Glasgow_Green" title="Glasgow Green">Glasgow Green</a></div></div><div class="tsingle" style="width:140px;max-width:140px"><div style="border:1;;height:82px;overflow:hidden"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:2018_at_Glasgow_Central_station_-_along_the_west_side.JPG" class="mw-file-description"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/2018_at_Glasgow_Central_station_-_along_the_west_side.JPG/250px-2018_at_Glasgow_Central_station_-_along_the_west_side.JPG" decoding="async" width="138" height="83" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/2018_at_Glasgow_Central_station_-_along_the_west_side.JPG/330px-2018_at_Glasgow_Central_station_-_along_the_west_side.JPG 2x" data-file-width="1366" data-file-height="820" /></a></span></div><div><a href="/wiki/Glasgow_Central_railway_station" title="Glasgow Central railway station">Glasgow Central</a></div></div></div></div></div></td></tr><tr class="mergedtoprow"><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data maptable"><style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1028600610">.mw-parser-output .ib-settlement-cols{text-align:center;display:table;width:100%}.mw-parser-output .ib-settlement-cols-row{display:table-row}.mw-parser-output .ib-settlement-cols-cell{display:table-cell;vertical-align:middle}.mw-parser-output .ib-settlement-cols-cellt{display:table-cell;vertical-align:top}</style>
